These monthly rock, pop and other music video collections started around 1987
and lasted until about 1995, when vhs started to geaux away. This features CT's
"You're All I Wanna Do", plus some MTV Europa stuff and everything from R & B
to metal songs from various bands. I just saw this last copy and bought it for Cheap
Trick. Most bands I was not familiar with. Got prompt service on it's delivery to my
post office box.
